OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1772463771
OL,3,CBritish expat in Dubai says 'only
OL,4,Cthing I want is to be on flight home'
OL,6,FA teacher living in Dubai says
OL,7,Funcertainty caused by conflict in the
OL,8,FMiddle East at the weekend means the
OL,9,Fonly thing she wants is to be "on a
OL,10,Fflight back to Newcastle".
OL,12,FChloe, who has lived in the Middle
OL,13,FEast for five years, told ITV News
OL,14,FTyne Tees that she had come to the
OL,15,Fdecision after a "terrifying" weekend
OL,16,Fof watching missiles intercepted in
OL,17,Fthe skies close to where she lives.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1772463771
OL,3,CBritish expat in Dubai says 'only
OL,4,Cthing I want is to be on flight home'
OL,6,FSpeaking on Monday (2 March), she
OL,7,Fsaid: "It's the uncertainty that's
OL,8,Fbringing a lot of fear I think. It
OL,9,Fseems to have calmed down a bit now -
OL,10,Fthe loud bangs and seeing the missiles
OL,11,Fin the sky and stuff like that.
OL,13,F"But the uncertainty of when things
OL,14,Fwill - you know will normality resume?
OL,15,FWill it ever feel the same here? I
OL,16,Fthink that's the real scare here for
OL,17,Fus."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
