PN,42103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1772463771
OL,3,CBritish expat in Dubai says 'only
OL,4,Cthing I want is to be on flight home'
OL,6,FChloe captured missiles being
OL,7,Fintercepted from the balcony window of
OL,8,Fher home near Dubai International
OL,9,FAirport
OL,11,FOriginally from Denton Burn in
OL,12,FNewcastle, teacher Chloe said her
OL,13,Fparents and siblings live on one side
OL,14,Fof the city while she lives on the
OL,15,Fother side, near to Dubai
OL,16,FInternational Airport.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
