OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1772463771
OL,3,CBritish expat in Dubai says 'only
OL,4,Cthing I want is to be on flight home'
OL,6,FAt the weekend, Chloe captured
OL,7,Fmissiles being intercepted from her
OL,8,Fbalcony window - and said debris from
OL,9,Fthe explosions fell just 400 metres
OL,10,Ffrom her home.
OL,12,FShe added: "Our life is here and we've
OL,13,Fbuilt a life here (but) at the moment
OL,14,Fthe only thing I want is to be on a
OL,15,Fflight back to Newcastle. So if that
OL,16,Fopportunity arises then I think we
OL,17,Fwould take that chance and leave as
OL,18,Fsoon as we could."
OL,26,@uD@SpmuD@Wpn
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
