FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1772463771
OL,3,CBritish expat in Dubai says 'only
OL,4,Cthing I want is to be on flight home'
OL,6,FMeanwhile Michael and Amy Appleyard
OL,7,Ffrom Tockwith, near York, are stranded
OL,8,Fon holiday in Dubai with two relatives.
OL,10,FThe experience of hearing missiles
OL,11,Fintercepted overhead has left the
OL,12,Fcouple feeling a "real sense of panic
OL,13,Fand danger".
OL,15,FMichael said: "We started hearing some
OL,16,Frumbles in the sky above which turned
OL,17,Fout to be the UAE air defence measures
OL,18,Fagainst the incoming Iranian missiles
OL,19,Fand drones.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1772463771
OL,3,CBritish expat in Dubai says 'only
OL,4,Cthing I want is to be on flight home'
OL,6,F"24 hours ago a missile's debris hit a
OL,7,Fhotel not far from us that we can see
OL,8,Foff our balcony and caused quite a big
OL,9,Ffire, which was very unnerving to see.
OL,10,FThere was a huge cloud of black smoke.
OL,12,F"Later that night the explosions got
OL,13,Fworse. They got louder and louder like
OL,14,Fthey were almost overhead. To the
OL,15,Fpoint the ground was shaking in our
OL,16,Fhotel room."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1772463771
OL,3,CBritish expat in Dubai says 'only
OL,4,Cthing I want is to be on flight home'
OL,6,FStranded tourists Amy and Michael
OL,7,FAppleyard said they felt a "real sense
OL,8,Fof panic and danger" after receiving
OL,9,Fan alert which was followed by loud
OL,10,Fbangs
OL,12,FMichael said they were then woken in
OL,13,Fthe early hours of Sunday by an
OL,14,Femergency alert on their phones.
OL,16,F"A few minutes after that there were
OL,17,Fthree of the loudest bangs I've ever
OL,18,Fheard directly above us and it truly
OL,19,Fshook the ground and the windows," he
OL,20,Fcontinued. "That's when we truly felt
OL,21,Fa real sense of panic and danger."
OL,26,@xD@AOU}D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
