OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1772463771
OL,3,CBritish expat in Dubai says 'only
OL,4,Cthing I want is to be on flight home'
OL,6,FThe couple are awaiting news of how
OL,7,Fthey will return home after their
OL,8,Fflight leaving Dubai on Tuesday was
OL,9,Fcancelled.
OL,11,FTravel expert Simon Calder shared his
OL,12,Fadvice for those unable to travel home.
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV News Tyne Tees, he
OL,15,Fsaid anyone trying to get home should
OL,16,Fget in touch with the airline they
OL,17,Fwere due to travel with to see what
OL,18,Fthey are able to provide "in terms of
OL,19,Falternative flights, hotel
OL,20,Faccommodation or meals".
OL,26,@zD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/9
