PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1772463771
OL,3,CBritish expat in Dubai says 'only
OL,4,Cthing I want is to be on flight home'
OL,6,FSimon added that travel insurance
OL,7,Fcompanies could also be contacted if
OL,8,Fairlines were unable to provide any
OL,9,Fsupport.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/9
